DESCRIPTION
===========

Robocodec is a high-performance robotics data format library for reading and writing MCAP
and ROS bag files. It provides efficient I/O operations, parallel processing capabilities,
and support for multiple message encodings (CDR, Protobuf, JSON).

PROJECT STRUCTURE
=================

- src/              - Core library source code
  - encoding/       - Message encoding/decoding (CDR, Protobuf, JSON)
  - schema/         - Schema parsing (ROS .msg, ROS2 IDL, OMG IDL)
  - io/             - I/O operations and format handlers
  - core/           - Core types and error handling
  - types/          - Arena allocation and memory management
  - rewriter/       - Data transformation and conversion

CONTRIBUTORS
